==制作==
[[File:Pendleton_Ward_at_the_Tomorrow_Show.jpg|thumb]]]]
短片由[[潘得顿·沃德|潘得顿·沃德]]主创。沃德此前曾就读于[[加州藝術學院|加州藝術學院]]，他称这一段经历影响了自己创作〈探險活寶〉的风格。<ref name=timeforsome/>角色扮演游戏[[龙与地下城|龙与地下城]]也是其灵感来源之一。<ref name="Screencrush"/>在沃德就读期间，[[尼克国际儿童频道|尼克儿童频道]]曾到加州艺术学院邀请学生用一分钟介绍自己的创意。他在展示中介绍了自己对〈探險活寶〉的最初构思，但未获得频道主管的认可。他毕业后，在这一构思的基础上逐渐完善，构想出一个男孩和一只狗在魔法世界拯救公主的故事。<ref name="AOOT">{{cite web|title=Adventure Time|url=http://www.artofthetitle.com/title/adventure-time/|publisher=Art of the Title|accessdate=2017-07-10|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160320084120/http://www.artofthetitle.com/title/adventure-time|archivedate=2016-03-20}}</ref>

{{le|弗雷德瑞特工作室|Frederator Studios}}开发部门副主管埃里克·霍曼（{{lang|en|Eric Homan}}）看过沃德在艺术学院期间创作的作品《制作人秀》（{{lang|en|The Producer's Show}}）之后主动联系沃德，邀请他为工作室提供新的创意。这是沃德自加州艺术学院毕业进入动画界的第一个工作。霍曼请沃德创作一部短片推销给{{le|尼克卡通频道|Nicktoons (TV channel)}}节目《{{le|随机卡通|Random! Cartoons}}》。<ref name=awnrandom/>这一节目由弗雷德瑞特工作室与[[尼克国际儿童频道|尼克儿童]]联合制作，播出动画制作人的原创短片，部分短片有机会制作成正式的动画剧集。<ref name="AOOT"/><ref>{{cite web|title=Random! Cartoons|url=http://frederator.com/series/random/|website=frederator.com|accessdate=2017-07-06|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170706013528/http://frederator.com/series/random/|archivedate=2017-07-06}}</ref>沃德花费一至两周的时间基本完成了《探險活寶》的[[故事板|故事板]]。他称创作时无法预知这部作品未来是否会成功，因此整个过程尤其“激动人心”。<ref name=awnrandom/>他坦承自己在构思时并未考虑其商业价值，能够成功“纯属运气”。<ref name="Screencrush">{{cite web|last1=Hayes|first1=Britt|title='Adventure Time' Interview: Creator Pendleton Ward and Star Tom Kenny|url=http://screencrush.com/adventure-time-interview/|website=ScreenCrush|accessdate=2017-07-10|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150914182816/http://screencrush.com/adventure-time-interview/|archivedate=2015-09-14}}</ref>

沃德完成故事板后，向工作室介绍作品时带着吉他自弹自唱了短片主题曲。<ref name=awnrandom/>工作室-{zh-cn:首席执行官; zh-hk:行政總裁; zh-tw:執行長;}-{{le|弗雷德·塞伯特|Fred Seibert}}坦言这一举动颇有新意，在展示中也开怀大笑，但他认为作品太像“学生作品”、“艺术片”，缺乏商业潜力，因此不愿制作这部短片。开发总监霍曼和制作总监凯文·科尔德（{{lang|en|Kevin Kolde}}）则与他意见相左，认为塞伯特的笑声已经足够有说服力，最终劝说他同意投入制作。<ref name=bleeding>{{cite AV media|last=Johnston|first=Rich|title=Grace Randolph's Between The Pages With Adventure Time's Fred Seibert|url=http://www.bleedingcool.com/2012/02/10/grace-randolphs-between-pages-adventure-times-fred-seibert/|publisher=Bleeding Cool|accessdate=2017-07-08|date=2012-02-10|time=3:58-6:11|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303215954/http://www.bleedingcool.com/2012/02/10/grace-randolphs-between-pages-adventure-times-fred-seibert/|archivedate=2016-03-03}}</ref>

沃德雇用了刚毕业于加州艺术学院的几位朋友一同参与制作，其中尼尔·格拉夫（{{lang|en|Neil Graf}}）负责上色，朱利安·纳里诺（{{lang|en|Julian Narino}}）负责设计背景，{{le|亞當·穆托|Adam Muto}}负责绘制道具。格拉夫在此之后加入动画《一家之主》（{{lang|en|King of the Hill}}）的制作，纳里诺转投[[萊卡_(動畫公司)|莱卡公司]]，穆托则留在《探險活寶》团队，成为正式剧集的[[執行製作人|執行製作人]]和编剧。<ref name=awnrandom>{{cite web|url=https://www.awn.com/animationworld/random-thoughts-frederator-cartoonists|title=Random Thoughts from Frederator Cartoonists|publisher=Animation World Network|first=Andrew|last=Farago|accessdate=2017-07-11|date=2009-01-29|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160718230250/http://www.awn.com/animationworld/random-thoughts-frederator-cartoonists|archivedate=2016-07-18}}</ref>短片于2006年制作完成，<ref>{{cite web|last1=Goldstein|first1=Rich|title=This Is How an Episode of Cartoon Network's 'Adventure Time' Is Made|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/this-is-how-an-episode-of-cartoon-networks-adventure-time-is-made|website=The Daily Beast|accessdate=2017-07-08|date=2013-12-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170709103950/http://www.thedailybeast.com/this-is-how-an-episode-of-cartoon-networks-adventure-time-is-made|archivedate=2017-07-09}}</ref>最终成品时长6分钟。<ref name="IMDb">{{cite web|title="Random! Cartoons" Adventure Time (TV Episode 2008)|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0784727/|publisher=IMDb|accessdate=2017-07-08|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170209211513/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0784727/|archivedate=2017-02-09}}</ref>

==播出、反响和后续==
〈探險活寶〉于2007年1月11日在{{le|尼克卡通频道|Nicktoons (TV channel)}}作为独立短片播出，<ref>{{cite web|title=Ahh! Look what we missed! Last Wednesday, 1/11,...|url=http://frederator-studios.frederator.com/post/156088287047/ahh-look-what-we-missed-last-wednesday-111|website=The Frederator Studios|accessdate=2017-07-08|date=2017-01-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170627202447/http://frederator-studios.frederator.com/post/156088287047/ahh-look-what-we-missed-last-wednesday-111|archivedate=2017-06-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=McDonnell|first1=Chris|title=Art of Ooo|date=2014|publisher=Harry N. Abrams|isbn=9781419704505|page=24}}</ref>随后被上传至[[YouTube|YouTube]]并迅速[[網絡爆紅短片|爆红]]，<ref>{{cite web|title=Watch Adventure Time On YouTube|url=http://archives.frederatorblogs.com/talk_to_the_snail/2007/01/16/watch-adventure-time-on-youtube/|website=Frederator Studios|accessdate=2017-07-08|date=2007-01-16|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180421101650/http://archives.frederatorblogs.com/talk_to_the_snail/2007/01/16/watch-adventure-time-on-youtube/|archivedate=2018-04-21}}</ref><ref name=timeenter>{{cite web|last=Feeney|first=Nolan|title=The Weird World of Adventure Time Comes Full Circle|url=http://entertainment.time.com/2013/03/29/the-weird-world-of-adventure-time-comes-full-circle/|work=Time|publisher=Time Inc.|accessdate=2017-07-08|date=2013-03-29|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170215102439/http://entertainment.time.com/2013/03/29/the-weird-world-of-adventure-time-comes-full-circle/|archivedate=2017-02-15}}</ref>一年内即获得300万次播放量。<ref>{{cite web|last=Seibert|first=Fred|url=http://adventuretime.frederator.com/post/462848254/and-the-hit-just-keeps-on-coming|title=And the hit just keeps on coming.|publisher=Frederator Studios|date=2008-04-04|accessdate=2017-07-08|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303195523/http://adventuretime.frederator.com/post/462848254/and-the-hit-just-keeps-on-coming|archivedate=2016-03-03}}</ref><ref name="rollingstone">{{cite web|last1=Strauss|first1=Neil|title='Adventure Time': The Trippiest Show on Television|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/tv/features/adventure-time-the-trippiest-show-on-television-20141002|publisher=Rolling Stone|accessdate=2017-07-08|date=2014-10-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141003001355/http://www.rollingstone.com/tv/features/adventure-time-the-trippiest-show-on-television-20141002|archivedate=2014-10-03}}</ref>2008年12月7日，短片在尼克卡通频道《{{le|随机卡通|Random! Cartoons}}》中重播。<ref name="IMDb"/><ref name=timeenter/><ref>{{cite episode| title=Adventure Time| series=Random! Cartoons|credits = Leichliter, Larry, Hugo Morales, & Pendleton Ward (directors); Pendleton Ward (writer) | network = Nicktoons |airdate=2008-12-07| season = 1 | number = 2b}}</ref>短片在美国动画界奖项第34届[[安妮奖|安妮奖]]中收获“最佳动画短片”的提名，但未能获奖。<ref>{{cite web|title=Awards :: 34th Annie Awards|url=http://annieawards.org/34th-annie-awards|publisher=ASIFA-Hollywood|work=AnnieAwards.org|accessdate=2017-07-09|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160322211430/http://annieawards.org/34th-annie-awards|archivedate=2016-03-22}}</ref>

试播集播出后获得成功，弗雷德瑞特工作室先后两次向尼克卡通频道推销这部作品，希望能合作制作成剧集在该频道播出，但两次都遭到拒绝。<ref name=timeforsome>{{cite web|last=DeMott|first=Rick|title=Time for Some Adventure with Pendleton Ward|url=http://www.awn.com/articles/2d/time-some-adventure-pendleton-ward|publisher=Animation World Network|accessdate=2017-07-10|date=2010-04-25|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100706102754/http://www.awn.com/articles/2d/time-some-adventure-pendleton-ward|archivedate=2010-07-06}}</ref><ref name="enchiridion">{{cite web|url=http://frederatorblogs.com/adventure_time/2010/04/22/the-enchiridion-storyboards/|title='The Enchiridion' Storyboards|publisher=Frederator Studios|accessdate=2017-03-18|date=2010-04-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100805002214/http://frederatorblogs.com/adventure_time/2010/04/22/the-enchiridion-storyboards/|archivedate=2010-08-05}}</ref>工作室于是转而联系[[卡通频道|卡通频道]]。卡通频道看过短片后乐意接手，但希望沃德能证明这部作品不仅仅是“昙花一现”，要求他以相同的风格继续推出新作。<ref name=enchiridion/>沃德重新梳理了短片的理念，希望能“完整展示”整个世界观，而不仅仅是最初表现出的“学前儿童风格”。<ref name=timeforsome/>在好友{{le|帕特里克·麥克海爾 (艺术家)|Patrick McHale (artist)|帕特里克·麥克海爾}}和{{le|亞當·穆托|Adam Muto}}的帮助下，沃德创作了一集[[分镜|故事板]]，内容是芬恩和泡泡糖公主约会共进[[意大利面|意大利面]]。<ref name=enchiridion/>但卡通频道对这一集并不满意，要求他重新创作，希望重现试播集中的“特殊之处”，例如主角的开场舞、“亚伯拉罕·林肯登场瞬间”、公主和英雄之间尴尬一吻等标志性场景。沃德于是创作出〈[[英雄寶典|英雄寶典]]〉一集的故事板，尽量还原了最初短片中的元素，获得频道的认可。2008年9月，卡通频道同意开始制作《[[探險活寶|探險活寶]]》的[[探險活寶_(第一季)|第一季]]。<ref name=enchiridion/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cartoonbrew.com/tv/cartoon-network-acquires-adventure-time-6753.html|title=Cartoon Network Acquires Adventure Time|first=Amid|last=Amidi|work=Cartoon Brew|publisher=Cartoon Brew LLC|date=2008-08-29|accessdate=2017-03-18|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308203926/http://www.cartoonbrew.com/tv/cartoon-network-acquires-adventure-time-6753.html|archivedate=2016-03-08}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://archives.frederatorblogs.com/adventure_time/2009/07/16/enchiridion-props-in-color/|title='Enchiridion' Props in Color|publisher=Frederator Studios|date=2009-07-06|accessdate=2017-03-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303204427/http://archives.frederatorblogs.com/adventure_time/2009/07/16/enchiridion-props-in-color/|archivedate=2016-03-03}}</ref>

